<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kitchen (START AGAIN)</title>
    <link href="/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all">
    <link href="https://isat-script-project.neocities.org/feed.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="ISAT Script RSS Feed!">
    <script src="/bars.js"></script> 
    <script src="/expressions.js" type="module" defer></script> 
    <script src="/search.js" defer></script>
</head>

<body>

    <help-er></help-er>

    <div id="container">
        <head-er></head-er>

        <div id="center">
            <side-bar></side-bar>

            <main>
                <h1>Prayer room (START AGAIN)</h1>
                <p><b>Source:</b> Map(unsure TODO) (Prayer room)</p>

                <br>

                <h1>Index</h1>

                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#statue">Mirabelle's statue</a></li>
                </ul>

                <hr>
                <br>

                <h1 id="statue">Mirabelle's statue</h1>

                <div class="dialogue">

                  <p class="dialogue-line">
                        (Their face obscured, Their silhouette shrouded, Their expression hidden...)
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        (An intact statue of the Change God stands before you.)
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                            <span class="dialogue-name">Housemaiden</span>
                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(pray_2)</span>
                        </span>
                        ...
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                            <span class="dialogue-name">Fighter</span>
                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(thinking_2)</span>
                        </span>
                        ...
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                            <span class="dialogue-name">Researcher</span>
                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(thinking_2)</span>
                        </span>
                        ...
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                            <span class="dialogue-name">Kid</span>
                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(pray_1)</span>
                        </span>
                        ...
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        (Most of your friends are sending their wishes to the Change God...)
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        (...)
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        (Join them?)
                    </p>


                    <ul class="dialogue-option">
                        <li>
                            <details>
                                <summary>
                                    Yes.
                                </summary>
                                <div class="dialogue">
                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        (You close your eyes and pray for rest.)
                                    </p>
                                  
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <details>
                                <summary>
                                    No.
                                </summary>
                                <div class="dialogue">
                                    <p class="dialogue-note">
                                        First loop
                                    </p>
                                  
                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        (You stay unmoving.)
                                    </p>
                                  
                                    <hr>
                                  
                                    <p class="dialogue-note">
                                        Second loop onward
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        (Not yours, not yours, not yours.)
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                                            <span class="dialogue-name">Fighter</span>
                                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(wondering_2)</span>
                                        </span>
                                        ...?
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        (He's looking at your clenched fists.)
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        (You relax, and flash him an embarassed smile.)
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                                            <span class="dialogue-name">Fighter</span>
                                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(annoyed_1)</span>
                                        </span>
                                        ...
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                                            <span class="dialogue-name">Fighter</span>
                                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(proud_1)</span>
                                        </span>
                                        ...Hey everyone, let's get going, 'kay???
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                                            <span class="dialogue-name">Housemaiden</span>
                                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(hmm_1)</span>
                                        </span>
                                        Oh! Um, okay...
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="dialogue-note">
                                        You get one weird point for this
                                    </p>
                                  
                                  
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                            <span class="dialogue-name">Housemaiden</span>
                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(pray_2)</span>
                        </span>
                        ...
                    </p>

                    <p class="dialogue-line">
                        <span class="dialogue-head">
                            <span class="dialogue-name">Housemaiden</span>
                            <span class="dialogue-expression">(smile_1)</span>
                        </span>
                        ...Let's go?
                    </p>


                </div>
                
            </main>
        </div>

        <foot-er></foot-er>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
